{"tid":1864158,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"星塵回憶錄 - 香港(三) 第一條人命，二百萬＋１","createTime":"2020-02-05T12:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T16:57:54.000Z","uid":94771,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ee988899913d0e054fb868c72467defbadb7da4c","tid":1864158,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:45:57.000Z","msg":"依個系列係比大家由開始回憶到現在，希望大家可以唔好忘記我地一直走的路<br />\n<br />\n第三集暫時去到6月13日到6月16日先<br />\n<br />\n６１２之後，引起各界極大的回響。最終果日被定性為暴動<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/pk77777-22_fkGiw_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpk77777-22_fkGiw_1200x0.png&h=45358823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且ＨＡ（醫院管理局）重聯網幫黑警捉香港人<br />\n社會終於得知黑警可以為政府殘害香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6月14日　香港的媽媽見一眾年青人在６１２的血與淚<br />\n<br />\n發起了香港媽媽反送中集氣大會<br />\n集會人坐爆整個<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">遮打花園</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/BG-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF01.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2FBG-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF01.jpeg&h=c0e3da96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6月15日   政府係612慘案之後宣佈為 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>暫緩</ins></strong></span> 修例<br />\n<br />\n同日，香港反送中運動出了第一條人命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/BG-cincainnews.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2FBG-cincainnews.jpeg&h=6f55384f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁凌杰義士係ＰＰ(太古廣場)抗議墮樓亡<br />\n<br />\n35歲的梁凌杰義士身穿黃色寫有「黑警冷血，林鄭殺港」八個大字的雨衣，突然爬出太古廣場外逾20米高的臨時工作平台位置，掛上白色橫額，上有「全面撤回送中，我們不是暴動，釋放學生傷者，林鄭下台，no extradition to China」字樣<br />\n<br />\n黑警同消房先後到場了解，消房人員不停游說梁凌杰義士返回安全位置<br />\n<br />\n大批市民及立法會議員鄺俊宇亦到場了解<br />\n<br />\n至近9時，梁凌杰義士係ＰＰＰＰ(太古廣場)一躍而下，送院搶救後最終不治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fakEVOnfFY8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfakEVOnfFY8&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=389b715e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fakEVOnfFY8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2019/06/6b5930334d2bea312c79fac4074ae406.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F6b5930334d2bea312c79fac4074ae406.jpg&h=fa4accca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為612事件，香港人大為憤怒＋梁凌杰義士對政府的死諫同抗議<br />\n<br />\n最終引發６月１６日　二百萬＋１人　破盡香港的遊行人數紀律，抗爭至現在，暫時重未有任何遊行人數可以再超越６月１６日的超級大遊行<br />\n<br />\n同時６１６引起國際社會的強烈關注<br />\n國際廣泛關注此遊行，翌日登《紐約時報》[與《華盛頓郵報》美國印刷版頭版。<br />\n此遊行的人數成為國際焦點<br />\n<br />\n而因為616大遊行對梁凌杰義士的道念，全部的遊行人士都身穿黑衣<br />\nBlackBloc戰衣 都因為咁形成<br />\n<br />\n<strong>鑑於遊行人士眾多，民陣提前於下午2時43分起步，比原定的下午3時提早，遊行隊頭手持寫有「痛心疾首」的白底黑字，以及寫有「撤回惡法」的黑底白字直幡。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Hong_Kong_Station_to_Central_Station_Access_overcrowded_20190616.jpg/1280px-Hong_Kong_Station_to_Central_Station_Access_overcrowded_20190616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F7%2F73%2FHong_Kong_Station_to_Central_Station_Access_overcrowded_20190616.jpg%2F1280px-Hong_Kong_Station_to_Central_Station_Access_overcrowded_20190616.jpg&h=074026ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/80/Hong_Kong_Demonstration_20190616_Causeway_Bay-1.jpg/1280px-Hong_Kong_Demonstration_20190616_Causeway_Bay-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F80%2FHong_Kong_Demonstration_20190616_Causeway_Bay-1.jpg%2F1280px-Hong_Kong_Demonstration_20190616_Causeway_Bay-1.jpg&h=e216a764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/30/June16protestTreefong17.jpg/1280px-June16protestTreefong17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F3%2F30%2FJune16protestTreefong17.jpg%2F1280px-June16protestTreefong17.jpg&h=b5165237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/85/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_11.jpg/1280px-190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F85%2F190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_11.jpg%2F1280px-190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_11.jpg&h=c9a36a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>悼念人士為梁凌杰義士排隊上香、躹躬</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/70/June16protestTreefong08.jpg/405px-June16protestTreefong08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F7%2F70%2FJune16protestTreefong08.jpg%2F405px-June16protestTreefong08.jpg&h=c9f01f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/June16protestTreefong07.jpg/405px-June16protestTreefong07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F0%2F08%2FJune16protestTreefong07.jpg%2F405px-June16protestTreefong07.jpg&h=b87507db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><br />\n遊行由中午行到晚上１１時解散</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9OQ-zJYh1Xo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9OQ-zJYh1Xo&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=f72c83a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9OQ-zJYh1Xo</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>特區政府表示<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人在6月16日晚上8時29分發表新聞稿，行政長官林鄭月娥就修例致歉，但沒有回應遊行主辦方民陣的任何一項訴求。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo; 政府明白市民遊行是出於對香港的關心和熱愛。<br />\n對於市民一直以平和、理性方式表達意見，行政長官清楚聽到...<br />\n政府重申並無重啟程序的時間表。<br />\n行政長官承認由於政府工作上的不足，令香港社會出現很大的矛盾和紛爭，令很多市民感到失望和痛心，<br />\n行政長官為此向市民致歉，並承諾會以最有誠意、最謙卑的態度接受批評，加以改進，為廣大市民服務。 &rdquo;<br />\n&mdash;&mdash; 政府發言人</ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再一次當你臭四</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n同時打後都因為咁而出現了經典的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">是你教會我們和平遊行是沒有用的</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2019/12/%E6%A8%99%E8%AA%9E-%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%A0%E6%95%99%E6%88%91%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%94%A8-20191202050031_152c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E6%25A8%2599%25E8%25AA%259E-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2594%25A8-20191202050031_152c.jpg&h=e9231d8a&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ab350cb21a9b3fd5efe81199f14f2e5ab89e987e","tid":1864158,"uid":233156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7541d19f9a325109d4a23fc1d68cbc4e2089f5","tid":1864158,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:51:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba10b3537ec44710b847c32891628ee10d0e8ec2","tid":1864158,"uid":94771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"前面集數<br />\n<br />\n星塵回憶錄 - 香港(一) <br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1856139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1856139</a><br />\n<br />\n星塵回憶錄 - 香港(二) 612大戰 <br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1860019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://l